	* yum/depsolve.py: removed wrongly named and redundant method call

2004-08-22  Seth Vidal <skvidal@linux.duke.edu>

	* yum/depsolve.py: removed old function stubs

2004-08-22  Seth Vidal <skvidal@linux.duke.edu>

